OL,3,CWar veteran to stop cleaning military
OL,4,Cgraves after government dispute
OL,6,FA war who restores and maintains
OL,7,Fgraves across Britain says he will no
OL,8,Flonger come to after a dispute with
OL,9,Flocal officials.
OL,11,FSteve Davies who served in the British
OL,12,FArmy adds that he is passionate about
OL,13,Fthe work which is voluntary and funded
OL,14,Fby donations.
OL,16,FSteve says every grave renovation can
OL,17,Fcost up to #500 and explains his
OL,18,Ffrustration after he was asked to
OL,19,Fchange his cleaning process.
