OL,3,CWar veteran to stop cleaning military
OL,4,Cgraves after government dispute
OL,6,FHe says: "This is not anger, it's just
OL,7,Fsadness.
OL,9,F"I can only think they are embarrassed
OL,10,Fthat an outsider has come and done
OL,11,Fthis and they haven't done it."
OL,13,FSteve started five years ago in the UK
OL,14,Fafter he discovered the overgrown
OL,15,Fgrave of an 18-year-old rifleman who
OL,16,Fwas killed six weeks before the
OL,17,FArmistice in 1918.
