OL,3,CWar veteran to stop cleaning military
OL,4,Cgraves after government dispute
OL,6,FHe branched out to Jersey, restoring
OL,7,Fmore than 80 graves across the island
OL,8,F- including Beverley Bloor's late
OL,9,Fsister's.
OL,11,FBeverley explains: "It means a lot to
OL,12,Fmy family.
OL,14,F"I am really pleased with the results,
OL,15,Fit looks as lovely now as it was when
OL,16,Fit was first done.
OL,18,F"I just find it sad really that he has
OL,19,Fbeen made to jump through hoops."
