OL,6,F"Subsequently, a call was received
OL,7,Ffrom a colleague of Mr Davies to
OL,8,Fconfirm they had discussed matters and
OL,9,Fdecided that they no longer wished to
OL,10,Fcontinue with the works they had
OL,11,Fplanned using the less aggressive
OL,12,Fcleaning methods.
OL,14,F"They did not believe they could
OL,15,Fachieve the finish and product they
OL,16,Fhave led their customers to expect."
